Package mru.tsc.model

Class Toy

java.lang.Object
mru.tsc.model.Toy
Direct Known Subclasses:
Animal, BoardGame, Figure, Puzzle
public abstract class Toy extends Object
The Toy class is an abstract class that holds the general parameters that a toy needs to have. Classes that represent a specific toy type will inherit from this class.
Author:
Kevin Luo and Shaina Anne Garrido
